    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at 99acres Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Software Engineer to strengthen our Aurangabad-based team.\n\nAbout 99acres Asia Pacific Associates:\n99acres Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 99acres Asia Pacific Associates!",
